<section class="hero">
    <h1>Battery cost and performance modeling — before you build cells</h1>
    <p>
        CellVision is a physics-grounded battery modeling tool for comparing
        lithium-ion and sodium-ion designs, materials, and manufacturing costs.
        Originally derived from BatPaC, now evolving into a full SaaS platform.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="#open">Download CellVision Open</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="#pro">CellVision Pro — Coming Soon</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>What CellVision does</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Compare Li-ion and Na-ion chemistries</li>
        <li>Evaluate cathode and anode material choices</li>
        <li>Explore cell design trade-offs</li>
        <li>Estimate manufacturing cost drivers</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="images">
        <img src="website-graphic.png" alt="CellVision screenshot">
